---
title: Teriyaki Plant-Based Mince & Pear Slaw Tacos with Crispy Shallots & Garlic Aioli
description: Sweet and savoury plant-based mince is the star of this crowd-pleasing meal. Easy and satisfying, the tacos come together in a snap, with lots of veggies for everyone to build their own and join in the fun!

